# ── LLM provider (powers the Ask chat + the parent report card) ──────────────
# Set ONE provider key. Auto-detected in this priority: perplexity > openai.
# Without any key, the app still works via curated fallbacks.
#
# Perplexity (OpenAI-compatible Sonar API) — get a pplx- key at perplexity.ai → Settings → API
PERPLEXITY_API_KEY=
# PERPLEXITY_MODEL=sonar            # or sonar-pro

# OpenAI API (platform.openai.com — NOT the ChatGPT subscription)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# Optional: force a provider explicitly (perplexity | openai)
# LLM_PROVIDER=perplexity

# Optional: Google Sheet login logging via an Apps Script Web App webhook.
# Set this to your deployed Apps Script /exec URL to append every login
# (timestamp + email) to your sheet. See README "Login logging → Google Sheet".
# Without it, logins still append to a local .login-log.jsonl file.
SHEETS_WEBHOOK_URL=
